  Locus:
    Page: 2
    Verse: 15
Tags:
  - Abundance
---
Abundance is a natural law of the universe. The evidence of this law is
conclusive; we see it on every hand. Everywhere Nature is lavish, wasteful,
extravagant. Nowhere is economy observed in any created thing. Prof usion is
manifested everywhere.
